!!【柯林斯英汉双解大词典】

:<div>

advice /ədˈvaɪs/

1. N-UNCOUNT If you give someone advice , you tell them what you think they should do in a particular situation. 建议 

例： Don't be afraid to ask for advice about ordering the meal. 别怕就点餐寻求建议。 

例： Take my advice and stay away from him! 听我的忠告，离他远点！

</div>

